The paper deals with the detection of copy-move forgeries in images, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses various algorithms and techniques used for image processing and analysis, which falls under the category of computer science and cryptography (cs.CR). The evaluation of different feature sets and their performance can be considered as a machine learning problem (cs.IR, cs.LG).
